<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Refleksi Diri - BEM Feedback</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/tailwindcss/2.2.19/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background-color: #F3F4F6; }
        .fade-in { animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease-in; }
        @keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-10px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="h-screen flex items-center justify-center p-6 fade-in">
    
    <div class="bg-white p-8 md:p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-xl max-w-lg w-full border border-gray-100">
        
        <div class="text-center mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800">Refleksi Akhir Periode 🤔</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mt-2">
                Jujur aja, data ini cuma dilihat BPH buat evaluasi bareng (Gap Analysis).
            </p>
        </div>

        <form action="/reflection" method="POST" class="p-8 space-y-6">
            
            <div>
                <label class="block text-gray-700 font-bold mb-2">1. Skala Kontribusi (1-10)</label>
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-2">Skala 1-10, seberapa besar kontribusi yang kamu kasih ke proker/kementerian semester ini?</p>
                <input type="number" name="self_score" min="1" max="10" required 
                    class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-300 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 outline-none text-center text-xl font-bold">
            </div>

            <div>
                <label class="block text-gray-700 font-bold mb-2">2. Value Check (Self-Growth)</label>
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-2">Apa hal yang udah kamu dapat selama satu semester ini di BEM?(Contoh: Skill baru, networking, relasi, atau pelajaran hidup)</p>
                <textarea name="self_growth" rows="3" required placeholder="Contoh: Saya memahami bahwa ketika menghadapi konflik, blablabla..."
                    class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-300 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 outline-none"></textarea>
            </div>

            <div>
                <label class="block text-gray-700 font-bold mb-2">3. Hambatan Utama</label>
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-2">Apa hal yang paling membuatmu susah bergerak/hambat kinerja semester ini?</p>
                <textarea name="obstacle" rows="3" required placeholder="Jujur aja: Akademik, Bosan, Masalah Personal atau Lingkungan BEM..."
                    class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-300 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 outline-none"></textarea>
            </div>

            <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-4 rounded-xl transition shadow-lg">
                🚀 Kirim Refleksi
            </button>
        </form>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
